{"tid":1220931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急呼籲\b］617大家一齊進行《幫阿婆執橙大行動》","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:02:57.000Z","uid":260765,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"494fff81a13db283a709ce9a9934a0762528ef95","tid":1220931,"uid":260765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"細細個，呀媽、老師同政府都教我地要幫阿婆餸橙。呢個係愛護他人既好表現，而且無任何暴力成分。<br />\n<br />\n當日2點半，我地要搵一個有心有力阿婆、一個紅色既穿窿買餸膠袋、777個橙。<br />\n然後，企係金鐘夏懿道，咁樣先可以比呢個世界知道人性係有幾偉大同光揮，成為一個良好既市民既好處。<br />\n再者，阿婆就會唔小心將777個橙由膠袋掉曬出馬路，然後大家就為左幫阿手，將d橙放番落個膠袋入面，但可惜個袋穿左，放極都唔小心跌曬出黎。不過唔緊要，有心唔怕麻煩，做善事不遺餘力，總有一日會執番曬d橙。"},{"pid":"a84bbce6b4dd1b9085b7178eaaf3bb335c3484e6","tid":1220931,"uid":260765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:58:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9831bd454554c8608e27447d6d40c431643ea3ce","tid":1220931,"uid":260765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e47b04e54ecf2ca51001dea3b2631bc42cfc7ffa","tid":1220931,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一日淋病唔撤回 一日都未成功！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"10f22786df9f9d516505d246b96b758c25978ed8","tid":1220931,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"跣撚死人咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23e558d76cb4655d471b03c293ef80bd162f58d","tid":1220931,"uid":260765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:01:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3068fc04732a23d2ee142d80474cea49edb97353","tid":1220931,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"呢個係最後一個留言 大家負評上一頁就得<br />\n唔好覆"},{"pid":"d629b4a9a6d2d3999338b3716dfc07014c1af8cc","tid":1220931,"uid":260765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply